title: Another Terrorist Is Dead | Guests: Matt Schlapp & Phillip Kline | 11/30/20
description:
Joe Biden twisted his ankle while “playing” with his dog. The Supreme Court slapped down NY Gov. Cuomo’s coronavirus limits on religious gatherings. Biden’s proposed climate czar, John Kerry, assured the World Economic Forum that the Great Reset would happen under Biden. Author Paul Kengor recaps the election hearing in Gettysburg that the media wouldn’t cover and how data from Rudy Giuliani made the crowd gasp. American Conservative Union chairman Matt Schlapp discusses how a huge court win for Trump could flip Nevada’s election results. The FBI is now interested in the Amistad Project’s election data, and director Phillip Kline ties it to Mark Zuckerberg. Iran’s top nuclear scientist was assassinated, and the media isn’t happy.
